{"tid":1747161,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"無得投票嘅同學仔聽日有咩可以做？","createTime":"2019-11-23T05:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T06:16:32.000Z","uid":277590,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"637c5c2d9ae742e0745ef52cfaef0523bea2f061","tid":1747161,"uid":277590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T05:54:56.000Z","msg":"1）今晚去阿爺阿嫲屋企嚟個廿四小時全天候family day<br />\n<br />\n2) 幫忙做哨兵觀察各區老人院有無旅遊巴岀車，有就上連登同tg講，該區選民就識做狗衝落去排隊<br />\n<br />\n3）如果你屋企阿爸阿媽係自私中立撚，就算係淺黃，你叫佢排三粒鐘去投票仲慘過叫佢去死。你不妨陪佢一齊係票站外排隊<br />\n<br />\n4）約埋班同學仔一齊去更新下連儂牆資訊<br />\n<br />\n切忌：著黑衫，單獨行事"},{"pid":"59a2efc5ad6b426589376750a39289e3b2c0c7f3","tid":1747161,"uid":277590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T05:57:40.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e089e18137987d9a59c61603a7a122665e11b3","tid":1747161,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T05:58:14.000Z","msg":"影低旅遊巴落車嘅人大頭相拍片提醒佢哋驗證可能進行非法賄選"},{"pid":"2a662f4991e39fe0d857856ee511b0910bf3996e","tid":1747161,"uid":314531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T05:59:31.000Z","msg":"做哨兵幫手鳩叫"},{"pid":"b0a08754aa810f18d9db5ce76e7449193b2f7791","tid":1747161,"uid":277590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:03:34.000Z","msg":"推手推一推唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都想多d同學仔睇到！<br />\n<br />\n佢地雖然無票，但佢地分分鐘可以憑一人之力，拉住兩票保皇黨唔俾佢地落街"},{"pid":"dad1a837c43489c3fc7043d96a87dede58342f2c","tid":1747161,"uid":237517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:05:31.000Z","msg":"做義工幫手做勢派傳單最實際<br />\n<br />\n見唔見保皇幾撚多人<br />\n<br />\n唔知頭唔知路好易比人海攻勢影響到"},{"pid":"7d8dd10d207638cdbdf8d4c27e4dabb19de1bda2","tid":1747161,"uid":277590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dad1a837c43489c3fc7043d96a87dede58342f2c","tid":1747161,"uid":237517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-2